# AI Training Data Pipeline

A Python ETL pipeline for cleaning, validating, deduplicating, and exporting AI training datasets.

This project demonstrates production-style data engineering for AI workflows, including raw data ingestion, validation, text cleaning, label normalization, bad-record handling, and structured export generation.

More details will be added as the project develops.
